flipout-ts
==========

This package is a TypeScript port of the FlipOut geodesic path-straightening
algorithm and supporting half-edge / intrinsic-triangulation infrastructure
from geometry-central:

    https://github.com/nmwsharp/geometry-central
    Copyright (c) 2017-2020 Nicholas Sharp and the geometry-central contributors
    Licensed under the MIT License (see LICENSE)

The algorithm is described in:

    Sharp, N., & Crane, K. (2020).
    "You Can Find Geodesic Paths in Triangle Meshes by Just Flipping Edges."
    ACM Transactions on Graphics (SIGGRAPH Asia 2020), 39(6).
    https://nmwsharp.com/research/flip-geodesics/

When porting, source files include a "// Ported from geometry-central:
<path>" reference so the lineage of every translated function is auditable.
